#: plugins/mqtt/src/plugin.vala:1098
msgid ""
"⚠ Server: Prosody (mod_pubsub_mqtt detected)\n"
"\n"
"Prosody's MQTT bridge does NOT support authentication.\n"
"Any client on the network can subscribe to topics.\n"
"\n"
"Recommendations:\n"
"• Restrict MQTT port via firewall\n"
"• Use TLS for encryption\n"
"• Do not publish sensitive data\n"
"\n"
"Topic format: <HOST>/<TYPE>/<NODE>"
msgstr ""
"⚠ Server: Prosody (mod_pubsub_mqtt erkannt)\n"
"\n"
"Prosodys MQTT-Brücke unterstützt KEINE Authentifizierung.\n"
"Jeder Client im Netzwerk kann Topics abonnieren.\n"
"\n"
"Empfehlungen:\n"
"• MQTT-Port per Firewall einschränken\n"
"• TLS zur Verschlüsselung verwenden\n"
"• Keine sensiblen Daten veröffentlichen\n"
"\n"
"Topic-Format: <HOST>/<TYPE>/<NODE>"

